            "title": "盤中速報 - 宣德(5457)股價拉至漲停，漲停價39.2元，成交2,226張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>宣德(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5457:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5457\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5457-TW</a>)09日11:23上漲3.55元，股價漲停報39.2元，委買11,000張、委賣409,000張，成交2,226張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為各式連接器.精密零組件. 成機及模組組裝。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>宣德(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5457:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5457\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5457-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲1.42%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲6.23%，短期股價無明顯表現。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+584 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+546 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-1 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+39 張</li> <li>融資增減：+36 張</li> <li>融券增減：0 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
